description:
GreenSquareAccord is looking to tender for the Supply of Materials for our in-house DLO team and wider Departments including: 
- Managed Store Access Solution: 
- Delivery and Counter Service (including enhanced delivery options and out of hours supply) 
- Stock holding, Stock Availability, Substitutions and Special Items;
- Price Management, Quarterly Price Files and Support Terms: 
- Van Stock Management;
- Innovative Solutions;
- Sustainability, Ethical Sourcing and Waste: 
- IT app and Invoi
